{
  "slug": "claude-api",
  "name": "Claude Api",
  "type": "skill",
  "description": "Build applications using the Claude API, Anthropic SDK, or Agent SDK with language-specific patterns and best practices.",
  "longDescription": "Covers **7 languages** (TypeScript, Python, C#, Go, Java, PHP, Ruby) plus `curl` examples. Includes dedicated guides for the **Agent SDK** (Python and TypeScript) with architectural patterns, and deep dives into **streaming**, **tool use**, **batches**, and the **Files API**. Shared references cover model selection, error codes, and live documentation sources. Each language guide provides idiomatic examples using the official Anthropic SDK for that platform.",
